113
00:12:06,700 --> 00:12:09,240
You used so many tricks in the past,

114
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:13,340
it made Imperial Brother unwilling to hear any more reports about Ruoxi,

115
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:16,120
