246
00:25:01,962 --> 00:25:04,144
came from my manor.

247
00:25:04,948 --> 00:25:06,606
Now that she's already gone,

248
00:25:07,660 --> 00:25:08,980
why can't I

249
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:11,500
see her!

250
00:25:13,540 --> 00:25:15,340
